                    <span>If you need a quick insight into airline business - BUY THIS BOOK. Rigas did a great job in explaining the difficult world of airline business to a dummy like me. Now, having a quite deeper knowledge, I am missing some in-depth information about the commercial side and route planning. Overall: a best buy.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Good book but a bit out of date</div>
